She spoke to Drum magazine after the news about the show was revealed."I am happy, busy and very content," she said.B has already started filming for the show and told the magazine that it's been a busy year."I'm the busiest I have ever been so juggling everything has made life busy. But I love to push myself so I am child about it."As one of the most sought after personalities in Mzansi there's no doubt Bonang's diary is always full.But more than ever before we've been seeing her and bae chillaxing and showing each other hard love. A post shared by AKA (@akaworldwide) on May 22, 2017 at 3:32am PDT